title: Big Announcement Week (Part 2)
description: Fellas recap a spectacular live event with FL Governor Ron DeSantis, laugh about Kamala's missteps and play a new game of VEEP or VP. The variety progrum announces yet another live event for later this week with House Republican Leaders. The event can be streamed here: https://www.republicanleader.gov/live/
